<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>not move a finger • not move a muscle</xh5><p> <i>not move a finger</i>—(also: not lift a finger) not make the slightest effort to do smth.: It is unbelievable but my husband will <u>not move a finger</u> to help me on the domestic front.</p><p> <i>not move a muscle—</i>1. remain perfectly motionless: Find yourself a comfortable, out-of-sight place to sit, keep quiet, and <u>don’t move a muscle</u>. <i>2. = not move a finger:</i> I can’t believe Christians would let a thing like this happen and <u>not move a muscle</u> to help her.</p> </entry>
